close_reason: "Full telemetry pipeline verified: client queue working, endpoint probe healthy, 9 Docker containers running, 29700 events in Postgres, dogfood events visible. Queue bloat issue documented separately as pm-ntr0."
body: "Client: events queued at ~/.pm-cli/runtime/telemetry/events.jsonl with attempt tracking and exponential backoff. pm health --check-telemetry probes healthz endpoint. PM_TELEMETRY_DISABLED=1 disables telemetry. Redaction works for recent max capture level events. Server: all 9 containers up and healthy. RabbitMQ has 0 pending messages with 1 active consumer. Postgres has events from 2026-04-25 to present. Dogfood events visible with source_context=dogfood in Postgres. Grafana at pm.unbrained.dev accessible. No secrets in repo (check-secrets.mjs passes)."
